body:
If you would like to support a more sophisticated JSON schema would you rather just utilize the format used by spaCy?

In that format your demo text would look like so:

```json
[
	[
		"this is the first text",
		{
			"cats": {
				"label1": true,
				"label2": false
			}
		}
	],
	[
		"this is the second text",
		{
			"cats": {
				"label1": false,
				"label2": true
			}
		}		
	]
]
```

This has the benefit of allowing text to have more than one label attached to it.
